DEVELOPING KULINARIINDONESIA : Adding Bootstrap
-----------------------------------------------

1	Adding Bootstrap

	> copy and paste css and javascrip to layouts/application file

	>> Styling table

		>> open: restaurants/index file, add:

			> add: <table class="table table-hover table-condensed">

2	Adding Navigation Bar

	> Add navbar to layouts/application file


3	Simplify The Codes

	>> 2 reasons to simplify the codes:

		1. Minimize the typo mistakes, easier to debug
		2. Simple codes, more readable

	>> Use Partials template to simplify the codes

		Note:

		Partial file start with _(underscore)

	>> Create partial file :
	
		layouts/_navbar.html.erb, 
		layouts/_footer.html.erb, and
		layouts/_bootstap.html.erb, 

		> move navigation, footer, and SDN Bootstrap to it
		> render them in the application file.






